'''拉脫維亞'''位於[[波羅的海|波羅的海]]的東海岸，因此飲食也受到其他波羅的海沿岸國家的影響<ref name="DailyLatvia">[http://www.dailylatvia.com/articles-cuisine.html "Latvian Cuisine."] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011032728/http://www.dailylatvia.com/articles-cuisine.html |date=2011-10-11 }} [http://www.dailylatvia.com Latvian Institute] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailylatvia.com/ |date=20201203065123 }}. Accessed September 2011.</ref>。拉脫維亞飲食常用的一些食材，如馬鈴薯、小麥、大麥、白菜、洋蔥、雞蛋、豬肉都是這一地區常見的農產品。拉脫維亞飲食通常脂肪含量較高，並且使用一定的香辛料。

[[豌豆|豌豆]]和[[火腿|火腿]]通常被视为拉脱维亚人的主菜。拉脱维亚人也食用[[酸模汤|酸模汤]]（{{lang-en|Sorrel soup}}）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Latvijas Institūts {{!}} Aktualitātes|url=http://www.li.lv/index.php?option=content&task=view&id=80&Itemid=487|accessdate=2021-02-19|work=www.li.lv|archive-date=2011-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011115936/http://www.li.lv/index.php?option=content&task=view&id=80&Itemid=487|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[拉脱维亚黑麦面包|Rupjmaize]]则是该国的主食之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Latvia {{!}} Tasting Europe|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014092158/http://www.tastingeurope.com/location/latvia|accessdate=2021-02-19|date=2017-10-14|work=web.archive.org}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Ethnic American Food Today: A Cultural Encyclopedia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DBzYCQAAQBAJ&q=Rupjmaize+staple+latvia&pg=PA364|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|date=2015-07-17|isbn=978-1-4422-2731-6|language=en|first=Lucy M.|last=Long|title=Ethnic American Food Today: A Cultural Encyclopedia|access-date=2021-02-19|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320104944/https://books.google.com/books?id=DBzYCQAAQBAJ&q=Rupjmaize+staple+latvia&pg=PA364|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

拉脱维亚人也有饮用[[啤酒|啤酒]]的传统，啤酒是拉脱维亚消耗最多的酒精饮料<ref>{{Cite web|title=世界卫生组织-2018年全球酒精与健康状况报告|url=https://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/handle/10665/274603/9789241565639-eng.pdf#page=294|accessdate=|author=Vladimir Poznyak;Dag Rekve|date=|format=PDF|publisher=|language=美国英语|archive-date=2019-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190315184841/https://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/handle/10665/274603/9789241565639-eng.pdf#page=294|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管在1924年，拉脱维亚总统[[雅尼斯·恰克斯特|雅尼斯·恰克斯特]]签署法律禁止国民[[酗酒|酗酒]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_12052278 |title=直逼俄罗斯，新冠后拉脱维亚成欧洲最能喝酒的国家？ |author=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]] |accessdate=2021-04-08 |archive-date=2021-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126041307/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_12052278 }}</ref>。但拉脱维亚国民喜好飲酒的風俗仍然保存下来。该国首都[[里加|里加]]自2011年起开始在五月末举行一年一度的“拉脱维亚啤酒节”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Latvia Beer Fest in Riga {{!}} Craft Beer Nomads|url=https://craftbeernomads.com/latvia-beer-fest-riga/|accessdate=2021-02-10|work=craftbeernomads.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321041020/https://craftbeernomads.com/latvia-beer-fest-riga/}}</ref>，[[啤酒节|啤酒节]]聚集了来自国内外的啤酒爱好者和拉脱维亚和世界各地的数十家啤酒厂，吸引了许多游客。[[里加黑香脂|里加黑香脂]]（{{lang-lv|Rīgas Melnais balzams}}）是拉脱维亚的一种传统酒类饮料，最晚出现于1752年<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Bitter: A Taste of the World's Most Dangerous Flavor, with Recipes [A Cookbook]|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sX8oAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT129|publisher=Potter/Ten Speed/Harmony/Rodale|date=2014-09-16|isbn=978-1-60774-517-4|language=en|first=Jennifer|last=McLagan|title=Bitter: A Taste of the World's Most Dangerous Flavor, with Recipes|access-date=2021-11-26|archive-date=2022-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423021058/https://books.google.com/books?id=sX8oAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT129}}</ref>。

